replies.body:
Spending money on the game does not entitle you to special privileges. You should be conscious of your actions in respect to how much you value your account. Rules still apply across the board, that's why they're rules.
On the note of full refund, what about the 'portion' of the product you've already used? If you ever used the champ you paid for, or the skin you paid for, how does that factor into a 'full' refund?
{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}
